Criticism of the stimulus plan = terrorist plot, criticism of Obama = anti-american, and the ability to think = danger to the state.<br />
<br />
 <br><BR><font size=1>05:59 06-04-2009</font></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=<a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a>'>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#C3E3FF' ><font class="bfont">i&#39;m confused, what does that mean? <br><BR><font size=1>05:44 06-02-2009</font><BR><BR>Play Versus (or FMA) against me online sometime. Dmail me for friend code!</TD></TR><TR><td width='4' bgcolor=#FFFFFF>&nbsp;</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B>boothwah </B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=boothwah '>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' ><font class="bfont">From the Washington Examiner:<br />
<br />
