 <br><BR><font size=1>16:43 06-01-2009</font></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=<a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a>'>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#C3E3FF' ><font class="bfont">That would be pretty smart. Sell it for 50 billion to the chinese, then spend 1 trillion developing a missle defense system and wall around fl to protect from the Chinese there.<br />
